oped which circumvents vac system will spread amongst 'cheating' community by delaying initial ban valve hopes identify ban many cheaters possible like any software detection system some cheats are not detected by vac remedy this some servers implement voting system which case players can call for vote kick ban accused cheater vac's success at identifying cheats banning those who use them has also provided boost purchasing private cheats these cheats are updated frequently minimize risk detection are generally only available trusted list recipients who collectively promise not reveal underlying design even with private cheats however some servers have alternative anticheats coincide with vac itself this can help with detecting some cheaters but most paid for cheats are designed bypass these alternative server-based anticheats release when counter-strike was published by sierra entertainment/vivendi universal games was bundled with team fortress classic opposing force multiplayer wanted half-life absolute redemption firearms mods on march planet half-life opened its counter-strike section within two weeks site had received hits on june first public beta counter-strike was released followed by numerous further beta releases on april valve announced that counter-strike developers valve had teamed up january valve began testing version counter-strike for os x linux eventually releasing update all users april reception reception aggregate scores aggregator score gamerankings 8920% metacritic 88/100 review scores publication score game revolution gamespot 84/10 ign 89/10 ] this section needs expansion you can help by adding february upon its retail release counter-strike received highly favorable reviews new york times reported that e-sports entertainment esea league started first professional fantasy e-sports league with game counter-strike some credit move into professional competitive team play with prizes major factor counter-strike's longevity success brazilian sale 